I don't think Jian Jie
would resort to this trick.

25
00:01:41,220 --> 00:01:41,980
What do you mean?

26
00:01:42,820 --> 00:01:43,620
Who are you accusing?

27
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:44,780
No.

28
00:01:45,060 --> 00:01:45,940
What I meant is

29
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:46,900
it might be a misunderstanding.

30
00:01:47,980 --> 00:01:49,020
A misunderstanding?

31
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:52,780
Ye Zhongjue.

32
00:01:52,780 --> 00:01:54,020
Your wife was in the warehouse today,

33
00:01:54,020 --> 00:01:55,460
counting Health Pots all afternoon.

34
00:01:55,620 --> 00:01:56,500
Now you tell me it was

35
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:57,820
a misunderstanding like it was nothing?

36
00:01:58,220 --> 00:01:59,140
It's normally a job

37
00:01:59,140 --> 00:02:00,780
for five people separated
in different areas.

38
00:02:00,780 --> 00:02:01,460
But me?

39
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:03,220
I counted them five times by myself.

40
00:02:03,220 --> 00:02:04,140
Over and over again.

41
00:02:04,140 --> 00:02:05,140
I was afraid to get it wrong

42
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:06,420
so Jian Jie could find fault with me.

43
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:08,180
Do you know how many

44
00:02:08,180 --> 00:02:09,380
mosquitoes your Jueshi Group has?

45
00:02:09,380 --> 00:02:10,980
Look how much they bit me!

46
00:02:11,060 --> 00:02:12,300
And here you are being sarcastic.

47
00:02:13,260 --> 00:02:14,020
All right.

48
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:15,140
I'm sorry.

49
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:16,620
You worked very hard today.

50
00:02:16,820 --> 00:02:17,340
How about this?

51
00:02:17,660 --> 00:02:19,060
I'll give you half a day off tomorrow.

52
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:20,340
You can rest at home.

53
00:02:22,620 --> 00:02:23,220
Do I get paid?

54
00:02:24,740 --> 00:02:26,340
In theory, that would be impossible,

55
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:27,260
but I will

56
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:28,220
pay you triple.

57
00:02:29,580 --> 00:02:30,060
Alright.

58
00:02:31,180 --> 00:02:32,100
Anyway, I counted correctly.

59
00:02:32,580 --> 00:02:33,660
She won't find any fault with me.

60
