108
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:41,700
You may need to ask Ms. Jian about that.

109
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:47,740
I did ask her to do it.

110
00:04:48,140 --> 00:04:48,980
Ms. Bai.

111
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:50,980
How about you tell us about

112
00:04:50,980 --> 00:04:52,940
the mess your husband
Mo Zhenfeng caused first?

113
00:04:58,540 --> 00:04:59,220
I'm sorry.

114
